      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am honestly so excited to show you this beauty! I\u2019ve taken such good care of this car\u2014it\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy. It\u2019s in truly flawless condition, kept tucked away in the garage and handled with so much love. Seriously, it looks and feels just like it did the day it left the showroom! No scratches, no dents, and it still has that wonderful new-car smell. It drives like a dream and is ready for a new home. You\u2019ve gotta see it in person to believe how perfect it is! \u2728",
