    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a concours-level specimen featuring the legendary S54 straight-six with factory-spec compression and valve clearances recently verified. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp gate transitions, paired with a subframe that has been professionally reinforced for structural integrity. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the car retains its original factory-honed handling dynamics via an untouched M-Variable differential and pristine suspension components. Zero VANOS rattle and a meticulous maintenance file make this a turnkey collector-grade vehicle for the discerning purist.",
