    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been kept in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, glass-like finish with zero rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks, further protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the leather bolsters are firm and uncreased, the dashboard is free of any UV fading, and it retains that distinct 'new car' scent. Every button, switch, and digital display operates with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been serviced exclusively by master technicians using OEM parts, with a thick binder of service records to prove its pedigree. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage is equally pristine. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously preserved piece of automotive history that drives as tightly and smoothly as the day it was delivered. Sold with all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
