      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a museum-grade example of the S54-powered icon. The 3.2L high-compression inline-six features factory individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system, both fully serviced to ensure peak volumetric efficiency and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically, this chassis has been future-proofed with documented subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement. Power is routed through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock, providing exceptional torque vectoring. The suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings, preserving the car\u2019s legendary lateral composure. Finished in Carbon Black, the paint depth is exceptional, complemented by a pristine interior free of typical bolster wear or trim delamination.",
